You can create the packages as following:

ulyaoth-tomcat6:
wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ulyaoth/repository/master/ulyaoth-tomcat/build-tomcat6.sh ; chmod +x build-tomcat6.sh ; ./build-tomcat6.sh

ulyaoth-tomcat7:
wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ulyaoth/repository/master/ulyaoth-tomcat/build-tomcat7.sh ; chmod +x build-tomcat7.sh ; ./build-tomcat7.sh

ulyaoth-tomcat8:
wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ulyaoth/repository/master/ulyaoth-tomcat/build-tomcat8.sh ; chmod +x build-tomcat8.sh ; ./build-tomcat8.sh

ulyaoth-tomcat8.5:
wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ulyaoth/repository/master/ulyaoth-tomcat/build-tomcat8.5.sh ; chmod +x build-tomcat8.5.sh ; ./build-tomcat8.5.sh

ulyaoth-tomcat9:
wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ulyaoth/repository/master/ulyaoth-tomcat/build-tomcat9.sh ; chmod +x build-tomcat9.sh ; ./build-tomcat9.sh

This should give you the following packages:
ulyaoth-tomcat
ulyaoth-tomcat-admin
ulyaoth-tomcat-docs
ulyaoth-tomcat-examples